name: tba-api-client
description: Promise Based TBA V3 API Client with Types

scripts.test: tsc test/test.ts types/* node_modules/@types/node/*.d.ts --target es2017 --module commonjs --moduleResolution node && echo transpiled && node test/test.js
scripts.build: tsc && node generator/APIGenerator.js && tsc client/genAPI.ts node_modules/@types/node/*.d.ts --target es2017 --module commonjs --moduleResolution node --declaration --declarationDir types

author: Tomas Rakusan
